1. Statement of Purpose

First of all. -Quality is what matter the most-
The purpose of this manual is to ensure and safeguard the quality of Trep Estimator.

2. Instructions
  1. Good programming practices should be used at all times.
  2. Code should be formatted in a strict manner. Great care must be taken to ensure easy maintaining of code.
  3. Each part of "Getting Started with Object Oriented Programming" "https://docs.joomla.org/Getting_Started_with_Object_Oriented_Programming" should be met.
